[SN]TITLE[SN]
Prestatyn man appears in court charged with bigamy

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has appeared in court charged with bigamy relating to a wedding in Conwy county in 2014.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 57-year-old, from Prestatyn, Denbighshire, allegedly entered an illegal form of marriage in Llandudno in June 2014.
He denied the charge when he appeared before a district judge at Llandudno Magistrates' Court on Thursday and was bailed until his trial.
